headline.main: HEALTH: Physical Fitness; Young Women Are Getting Fatter, Study Finds

byline.original: By WARREN E. LEARY, Special to the New York Times

docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: Young American women, but not men of similar age,have generally been getting fatter for several decades, recently published findings suggest. The researchers say this is the first data to indicate such a trend.
